column2: Shake your left hands in the air 8 times while counting to 8.
Do it as fast and loud as you can.
Repeat with your other hand. Then do it for each foot.
Do it 7 times, then 6 times and continue until you get to 1.
Everyone calls out “Crazy chicken” when you’re finished and does their best crazy chicken dance!",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,36c0c171-5304-4183-904d-16715e564910,,execute_actions,;
